data.description: This wonderful full brick ranch home is on a level lot in the super convenient Oak Park Neighborhood!  With a fully renovated hall bath, a new HVAC unit in 2023, & a new roof in 2018, this home is ready for living. Also, the washer, dryer & kitchen refrigerator to remain.The nicely updated home features three bedrooms & 1.5 baths at a budget-friendly price. The private back yard has a new privacy fence. There is lots of storage in the detached garage. The galley kitchen has updated appliances, granite countertops, and a large laundry room with storage. Super easy access to 565, Land Trust Trails/Monte Sano Mtn, Downtown Huntsville, or Huntsville Hospital locations.
